tourBios.curYrHigh: Earned PGA TOUR Latinoamérica conditional status with a T13 finish at the Bogota, Colombia Q-School in January.
tourBios.personal: Has one brother, Brad... Earliest golf memory is playing golf with his father... If not a professional golfer, says he would be a professional basketball player... Michael Jordan is his favorite athlete outside of golf... The Orlando Magic is his favorite professional team... Personal motto: "Everything happens for a reason."... Would like to trade places for a day with Leonardo Di Caprio... His father, Michael Jordan and Bill Murray would round out his dream foursome.
